message.body: Hi! Questions: are you free Saturday afternoon and evening? If so, would you be interested in helping me move into my apartment for $8/hr? My dad says he is "getting old" and told me to ask my friends for help :) also how is your summer going so far? :)
Hey! I'm going to be on vacation on Saturday. Sorry :( summer is going well. Work hasn't started so it's been relaxing. How are you?
